cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.CY 

The paper discusses a mechanism for plausible deniability of sensitive data stored on devices, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also introduces a new write-only ORAM construction, which is a data structure related to data storage (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the performance of the proposed mechanism, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
